ue not accurate when custom filter the date.<br \/>\n* Fixed: survey sending to staff mail list fatal error.<br \/>\n* Fixed: pdf status not showing on utf8 charachters.<br \/>\n* Fixed: when deleting ticket deletes all custom fields values for tickets.<br \/>\n* Fixed: single ticket problem on some mysql versions.<br \/>\n* Fixed: Converting related expense to project the created invoice is not auto related to the project.<br \/>\n* Fixed: Expenses table not converting the dates to the selected dateformat.<br \/>\n* Fixed: Expense amount not includes tax in the list table.<br \/>\n* Fixed: Showing all tickets instead only customer tickets in customer profile.<br \/>\n* Fixed: Added some missing translation keys in the languages other then English.<br \/>\n* Fixed: Leads Kanban search error.<\/p>\n<p>* Small bugs fixed<br \/>\n* UI &amp; Responsivness Improvements<br \/>\n* Code Improvements<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Changes made in the main Perfex CRM theme. * Added option to choose pdf document format LETTER or A4. * Added 75% Polish translation. * Added option to swap Company\/Customer Details (company details to right side, customer details to left side) * Added option to choose invoice\/estimate PDF text color. * Added option to directly [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[23],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-754","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-changelog"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/754","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\